                  </p>
                  <p xml:id="footnote-2">
                      [2]. <bibl><ptr target="Georgiou2019"/>, here p. <citedRange unit="page">521-522</citedRange></bibl>. For an attempt to establish a list of the archbishops of Cyprus in chronological order, see also <bibl><ptr target="Laurent1948"/>, here p. <citedRange unit="page">164</citedRange></bibl>.</p>
                  <p xml:id="footnote-3">
                      [3]. <bibl><ptr target="PBW"/>, <citedRange unit="entry"><ref target="http://pbw2016.kdl.kcl.ac.uk/person/Basileios/20370/">Basileios no. 20370</ref></citedRange></bibl>. See also <bibl><ptr target="Laurent1948"/>, here p. <citedRange unit="page">162</citedRange></bibl>.
